metadata.name: SPHERE C:0X OBJEKTS : TERRAMETA-OBJKT-KEY
metadata.description:
Sphere C:0X Objekts are in a new phase and this is the TERRAMETA-OBJKT-KEY. 

First introduced as individual NFTS in 2021, initially 7 Objekts were designed to be CHROMA-tic landscape sculptures displayable in a larger gallery. Each sculpture a garden to be placed within a larger garden. 

Now the TERRAMETA-OBJKT-GARDEN will be opened on a SPATIAL 3D space. Stepping inside a space will be stepping inside each actual NFT. An NFT within an NFT. The GARDEN of course is token gated and this is the only KEY. Once the GARDEN is open, use this key to enter and enjoy the SPHERE C:0X OBJEKTS and find undiscovered NFT Sphere Objekts.
